                    text: "The TEL schema-for-schemas. Self-describing: parsing this document under the",
                },
                Comment {
                    text: "schema it defines yields a valid semantic model. The vocabulary is specified",
                },
                Comment {
                    text: "in §20.5 of the TEL Specification.",
                },
